{"block1":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Common colds usually come with symptoms such as coughing, sneezing, and itchy, watery eyes. But people with allergies experience this all the time, perhaps in a milder&nbsp;form. The information in this article should help you to overcome these uncomfortable symptoms and avoid their triggers.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you are having frequent allergy problems, your pet could be the problem. However, don&#39;t assume your pet is the cause before visiting an allergist to get tested. You will not necessarily need to find a new home for your pet, though you might need to alter your arrangements somewhat.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"\/images\/portrait-of-an-air-purifier.jpg\" class=\"img_left \" alt=\"portrait of an air purifier\" style=\"float: left; padding: 8px; padding-left: 0;\" \/>&nbsp;Apart from certain&nbsp;conditions, dust mites are almost impossible to avoid. These vile organisms thrive on dead skin as they burrow into your mattress and pillows. Talk about a nightmare! To combat these nuisances, encase mattresses and pillows in special zippered mattress covers and pillow cases. Then, wash your bedding weekly in hot water, as this can kill dust mites.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The fewer rugs and less carpeting you have in your home, the better. No matter how much you try to clean them, they can harbor allergens. If you want rugs to add some softness to a room, be sure you can wash them to remove allergens.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you are allergic to airborne particles, consider&nbsp;purchasing an air purifier with an integrated <a href=\"http:\/\/www.webmd.com\/allergies\/hepa-filters-for-allergies\"  >HEPA filter<\/a>. Using these filters will help lessen allergens that cause allergies. Look for a brand with a filter that can be cleaned to save money on buying disposable filters every month.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">People who experience allergies to foods, such as peanut butter and strawberries, can manage their allergies effectively by simply avoiding these foods.&nbsp;On the other hand, dealing with allergies to substances like pollen and pet dander can prove more difficult to handle. If you keep the tips presented here in mind, you will be better able to <a href=\"advice-you-need-to-know-if-you-have-allergies\"  >control your allergy symptoms<\/a>.<\/p>\r\n"}